casebody.data:
WASATCH COUNTY, UTAH, et al., petitioners,
v.
UTE INDIAN TRIBE OF THE UINTAH AND OURAY RESERVATION. No. 15-640. Supreme Court of the United States March 21, 2016.

Motion of Myton City for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.
